{"tid":318842,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPad Pro 10.5 Apps討論區","createTime":"2017-07-12T11:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T09:15:07.000Z","uid":74850,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28337a8a93742548c422c824de3d309e799e74af","tid":318842,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"配Apple Pencil真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n<br />\nDrop notes N edit PDFs:<br />\n<br />\n原生notes：update左IOS11PB, 可以影相scan文件真係好正。以前要另外開隻app整，scan完upload,再開第隻app寫野，依家方便好多，而且四邊位auto拉得幾好，即刻就del左個scanner app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但如果想手寫，暫時（好似）只可以當sketch, 冇inline<br />\n<br />\nNebo: 士多D精靈介紹先知呢隻野，識得將hand writing轉typing, 畫chart都轉到，第一次見覺得好新奇。但手字寫得衰會辨識唔到<br />\n<br />\nUPAD 3: 分左好多種唔同用途既notes, 但唔係好慣佢個UI, 硬係唔知佢d制係咩用途咁，冇咩耐性放棄左<br />\n<br />\nAdobe Acrobat: 最基本edit PDF既功能，當然唔夠用<br />\n<br />\nPDF Office (by Readdle): 可以auto將PDF上面要填野既位置變左fill in blank格仔，呢樣就係我要搵既野啦！！唔洗自己逐個Text box執落去/執位/對齊，即刻可以save做常用既PDF表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEvernote: 由iPad Air開始就好似好多functions咁, 又話sync落其他devices好方便。但咁耐以黎，次L次開個app都覺得lag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....結果冇用過<br />\n<br />\n隔離post見好多人推介Notabilty同GoodNotes, 仲有Affinity Photo同Procreate都好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有用開既巴絲可以分享多少少<br />\n<br />\n另外，有冇ching可以講下PDF Office同PDF Expert有冇唔同，睇下應該subscribe邊隻好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb618ed18c9a7b1c7f4498d64acbe4891f6d505f","tid":318842,"uid":22896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"Notability <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e568f3b2ec95869b1ebd5a5475910102559f92","tid":318842,"uid":18210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"Good notes"},{"pid":"4663d53bbcc4ae93e67da215f19d6aa543a8bc44","tid":318842,"uid":74850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"想知goodnote同notability分別係邊"},{"pid":"38cf45c90cec6e6f0f8e045a2b2cadf43ea685b0","tid":318842,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"等ios 11 ."},{"pid":"8ad8ad9e6146a968f138bbf364fa57191b0f5609","tid":318842,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等ios 11 .</blockquote><br />\n等唔切，用緊PB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232a7e76ae688c531aae59c7be911a04b8ef3f88","tid":318842,"uid":3899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"有GoodNotes 4, notability, Affinity Photo同Procreate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未用得晒 遲少少再分享下"},{"pid":"7b999caebdb24adf7e8ff46b01b961b2f1416303","tid":318842,"uid":74850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T22:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有GoodNotes 4, notability, Affinity Photo同Procreate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未用得晒 遲少少再分享下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86325aa